---
title: Prosciutto & Apple Arugula Salad with Feta, Pecans & Balsamic Glaze
description: A crisp, refreshing salad that hits all the notes—peppery arugula, juicy apple, salty prosciutto, and tangy feta. Pecans bring the crunch, while a drizzle of balsamic glaze adds a sweet-tangy finish that makes every bite pop!
